    "The identified productive entities also hold potential as exemplars and potential collaborators for researchers.",
    "Moreover, there is room to enhance and deepen academic partnerships, leading to a more comprehensive exploration of the benefits and hurdles of AI, particularly those rooted in deep learning, to multimodal data fusion in order to optimize decision-making.",
